<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5265> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5265" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Legate under Caesar in Gaul. Killed in the revolt of the Eburones (Caes. BG 5.24.5, and 26.1-37.7, and 39.1, and 53.4; Liv. Per. 106; Plut. Caes. 24.1; Flor. 1.45.8; Dio 40.5-6; Oros. 6.10.1). See above, on Aurunculcius Cotta." ;
	dprr:hasID 5265 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5212> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5212" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Legate under Caesar in Gaul (Caes. BG 4.22.5, and 38.3)." ;
	dprr:hasID 5212 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5165> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5165" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Legate under Caesar in Gaul (Caes. BG 3.11; Dio 39.45.1), where he crushed a rising of the Venelli, Curiosolites and the Lexovii (Caes. BG 3.11.4, and 17-19; Frontin. Str. 3.17.7; Dio 39.45; Oros. 6.8.18)." ;
	dprr:hasID 5165 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5108> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5108" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Legate under Caesar in Gaul (Caes. BG 2.5.6, 9.4, and 10.1; cf. Dio 39.1.4)." ;
	dprr:hasID 5108 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5065> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5065" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Legates under Caesar in Gaul. The four unnamed Legates in Caesar's battle with Ariovistus probably were among these (BG 1.52. 1). See 57, Legates; and esp. D.-G. 3.696ff." ;
	dprr:hasID 5065 .
